{"tid":1479291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] 817/ 818 捉狗/蝗攻略","createTime":"2019-08-17T00:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T03:30:09.000Z","uid":50936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8131517639cb4e237cc701839e08a83a15675aec","tid":1479291,"uid":50936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:05:11.000Z","msg":"為防再內狗同蝗混入， 大家一定要一team 一team 行動， 到步後， 最好幾個人一 team, 最好唔好分散<br />\n另外， 以下係25特徵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8T2DxW3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8T2DxW3.jpg&h=626ecc06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有， 捉蝗最易， 見有疑似蝗  可以上前問佢， 689 全名係乜， 777 全名係乜， 貪曾全名係乜<br />\n答唔到 (或唔出聲）就一定係蝗， 就算答到，佢地多數唔識講廣東話， 一開聲就穿崩<br />\n<br />\n最後一句， 大家一定要小心"},{"pid":"a9f4b779c9327fa2c702f50fc08e2b1ee084dfe7","tid":1479291,"uid":50936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:05:58.000Z","msg":"(轉)請廣傳 『如何從身體語言辨別警察』<br />\n「身體語言是不會騙人的」。<br />\n<br />\n你可以扮示威者，但改不了身體語言。有前警員寫過一篇 &quot;Police Body Language and Behavior&quot;，教你在人群中，一眼認出差人，話「差佬有樣睇」，就係咁解。<br />\n<br />\n這樣出色的臥底，無論在什麽地方，都會好似漆黑中嘅螢火蟲一樣，那樣鮮明，那樣出衆，架嘛<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n加入公民抗命，請入真正屬於香港人既巴絲打主群 (唔係石仔果個):<br />\n1號群-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/buyeasyjob/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fbuyeasyjob%2F&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75eDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=603d9588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/buyeasyjob/</a><br />\n2號群-&gt; <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/BroSisOn99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FBroSisOn99%2F&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75eDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=dbc093a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/BroSisOn99/</a><br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n【緊急幫義士】用Youtube影片廣告化為贊助！你看youtube片,我們捐錢，以無限為有限，以無法為有法！<br />\n現時進度係2122/4000小時<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTqygLer82cl5hmh0tMql_w/live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCTqygLer82cl5hmh0tMql_w%2Flive&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75eDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=a5de68f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTqygLer82cl5hmh0tMql_w/live</a>"},{"pid":"7ca53c0b058da4343cb89fca1133d78a34d7510d","tid":1479291,"uid":50936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:07:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"589c8fe564b6ec85f0fd67470216bed55151c94e","tid":1479291,"uid":50936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:09:12.000Z","msg":"出發前<br />\n1. 衣著: Black Boc 舒適為主 + 背囊<br />\n2. 電話鎖匙銀包<br />\n3. 線+尿袋<br />\n4. 水+零食<br />\n5. 雨傘<br />\n6. 防曬<br />\n7. 帽+太陽眼鏡 (防曬用 用雨傘遮太陽要拎足幾粒鐘同埋可能整到人)<br />\n8. 風扇仔<br />\n9. 退熱貼<br />\n10. 口罩<br />\n11. 食飽痾飽<br />\n(以防萬一)<br />\n12. 用散銀 勿用八達通<br />\n13. 新身份證放RFID卡套<br />\n14. 手機熄GPS, 請改用密碼解鎖 勿用Touch/Face ID<br />\n<br />\n出發後<br />\n交通係會塞硬 需要耐性 巴士就排長龍 地鐵就會塞到行唔郁 仲有時會飛站 <br />\n建議提早少少出門"},{"pid":"566da88e4b34b7a546404181fb102549accdf2c2","tid":1479291,"uid":50936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:10:37.000Z","msg":"機場個日， 捉一隻鬼，十多人捉，成百人圍，搞幾個鐘。<br />\n<br />\n確認係鬼，自身安全，扎起先算，鮮色噴油，畫記為鬼。<br />\n2<br />\n0"},{"pid":"00a87aee06b2813ca498fc5067f847d274d4cc30","tid":1479291,"uid":50936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQUFMjY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQUFMjY.jpg&h=1988781e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b96d6f7ad4a1cdef43ef32c4a5360f487d2194c","tid":1479291,"uid":50936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56a55d7c3ef1e3ccab9cda724abfa8f13bb0e3fb","tid":1479291,"uid":50936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r